{"tid":1120584,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[無式] [時空科普] 講下Mach's principle","createTime":"2019-04-22T18:26:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-24T15:26:26.000Z","uid":147721,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"a5f2546b4763717483d0d8e3f89c1af902517e8a","tid":1120584,"uid":147721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T18:26:07.000Z","msg":"開波之前講五點<br />\n<br />\n1. 唔好quote長文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 唔明既巴絲 可以去公立圖書館 借閱關於牛頓力學 狹義相對論 同廣義相對論既教科書先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 由於我要返工 所以之後都只係會有心情有時間先會出po<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/chicken3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而且topic係跟我心情 唔一定好連貫 大家唔好對後續有期望<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n4. 今次呢個po比較簡略 亦都相對唔係着重學術<br />\n而我係打算圍爐取暖 唔中意泥漿摔角<br />\n所以希望覺得研究物理無式無問題既各位 請你地直接block我上一頁<br />\n咁我地都可以互相慳返啖氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n另外有啲位講得簡份簡略/唔精準 大家都將就下 因為呢篇係科普<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n5. 我以前講過既野: <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n[有式] [分析力學] 講下拉格朗日力學 Lagrangian mechanics<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/570249\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/570249</a><br />\n[有式] [分析力學] 講下Lagrangian to Hamiltonian<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1005131\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1005131</a><br />\n[有式] [分析力學] 講下Hamiltonian Mechanics<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1035839\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1035839</a>"},{"pid":"f68da1c97d18f7fbbd86e2377e737ec54bb34646","tid":1120584,"uid":147721,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T18:27:28.000Z","msg":"今次我地罕有咁試下唔講式 講啲高大上既時空<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n首先問下大家 知唔知相對性原理係邊個提出黎既呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無錯喇 相信大家都好耳熟能詳 個個就係大名鼎鼎既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Galileo Galilei</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nGalileo最早提出 你係一隻密封既船入面 而隻船好平穩無搖既 你係分唔出隻船有冇行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然Galileo提出左相對性原理 論證無絕對既靜止/移動<br />\n但係Newton就覺得 &quot;你地收皮啦 我先最勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&quot;<br />\n於是Newton提出左佢著名既水桶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢話 假設有桶水均速旋轉緊<br />\n就算你跟住佢一齊轉 個桶望落去係靜止無轉到<br />\n但係你仍然會見到啲水飛去桶邊<br />\n所以你班柒頭收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個就係相對空間同絕對空間 早期既論點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"323841ab6d527d966a63bcab26009b8c1ce50dc9","tid":1120584,"uid":147721,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T18:28:34.000Z","msg":"之後兩派人各有各玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n直到1862年James Clerk Maxwell計到電磁場既傳播速度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家開始問 呢個係相對於咩既速度呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔通係相對光既速度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係做實驗發現 無論光源點郁法 光速都係同一數值啵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n於是大家就覺得 Maxwell條式錯啦屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係Maxwell equation做既prediction又全部都啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有人就提出 呢個速度係介質速度黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係又有人做實驗 發現測量唔到介質運動對光速既影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而物理哲學上 空間到底係相對定絕對 就更加混亂喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/superman.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n光速係如此既絕對得黎(做咁多實驗次次都不變) 又完美咁包容相對派既觀點(觀測者郁唔郁都係見到同一個光速)<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個問題經過好多人既研究 最後Albert Einstein提出佢既不變論 將相對性原理同光速不變融合埋一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過大家中意叫呢個理論做相對論多啲<br />\n但係呢個理論 仍然無解釋到點解慣性運動係相對 而旋轉就係絕對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dc3a7ea006a20d9797e3e5b4861f7cc1f2279a0","tid":1120584,"uid":62527,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T18:30:29.000Z","msg":"Lm<br />\n切勿quote長文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db832ed6471d345afa6b22ef371f5a3049331e63","tid":1120584,"uid":147721,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T18:30:55.000Z","msg":"Ernst Mach 馬赫數個個馬赫 就覺得其實旋轉都係相對 而且提出左佢既星星論證<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<blockquote>You are standing in a field looking at the stars. Your arms are resting freely at your side, and you see that the distant stars are not moving. Now start spinning. The stars are whirling around you and your arms are pulled away from your body. Why should your arms be pulled away when the stars are whirling? Why should they be dangling freely when the stars don't move?</blockquote><br />\n佢既意思係話 你自轉個時對手感到離心力 唔係因為咩絕對空間 而係因為你相對星星轉緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n反過黎講 如果唔係你自轉 而係星星圍住你轉 你都會感受到離心力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢既principle浪漫得黎 亦都對好多物理學家有巨大吸引力 Einstein都話佢既GR係受到Mach's principle啟發"},{"pid":"c380cd08a3624fd5d055e68634aaeefdf755fd24","tid":1120584,"uid":147721,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T18:32:32.000Z","msg":"大家係咪覺得 唔駛用式同數同深term 就學識相對空間既自己好叻叻豬呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n恭喜大家<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>唔係呀 你唔叻豬呀</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nMach's principle雖然叫principle 不過佢既表達完全唔具體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要具體寫出黎既 可以寫到幾十種唔同強度既陳述<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nwiki有Mach0到Mach10 因為有術語我就唔係科普po到列出黎了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而且General Relativity並唔係完全符合Mach's principle<br />\nG&ouml;del&rsquo;s universe係一個&quot;旋轉&quot;既GR solution<br />\n大家想用一條浪漫而簡單既句子 去說明時空性質既嘗試 落空了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n目前最能夠說明時間性質既 唔係Newton既&quot;我話絕對就絕對&quot;<br />\n唔係Mach浪漫既&quot;無絕對 你係相對星星轉&quot;<br />\n亦唔係兒登仔掛係口邊既&quot;一齊都係相對&quot;<br />\n而係Einstein field equations<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c849784a8d941c0fc0505cf4b582b4b57c50c113","tid":1120584,"uid":147721,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T18:35:54.000Z","msg":"呢個po既正文就去到呢到<br />\n希望睇到呢到既大家 可以係呢個無式既學唔到野既po入面<br />\n係我因為無式同數 而完全解釋唔到點解GR唔係完全Machian既情況下<br />\n學識到點解時空唔係絕對 亦唔係Machian既相對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可能大家覺得 下講完喇 講左啲咩呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我係結尾recap比大家聽<br />\nMach's principle講緊 你轉個時有離心力 係因為你相對遠方既星星轉緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">而且如果你要求無式無term要即食科普 就係好合理咁咩都講唔到</span>"},{"pid":"3e2d50085c6cbb5f33e20a13cea82a4716c50ede","tid":1120584,"uid":88263,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T19:05:11.000Z","msg":"<img src